01:20:21.258 --> 01:20:28.711
Everybody always listens to voices. Test it. Get in the Word and get centered with the Holy Spirit inside of you.

01:20:28.712 --> 01:20:50.349
Say, "Father, I thank You that I hear Your voice and a stranger's voice I'll not follow."All those forebodings and torment all the time that the devil will try to plant on you to put you in fear, saying, "Hey, you should be in fear all the time."You walk around, like I said, like you have an umbrella over your head, "Oh no, everything—the sky is falling, Chicken Little."And you go, "No, it's not falling.

01:20:50.350 --> 01:20:54.225
We've become more—we're more than conquerors through Him who loved us.

01:20:54.226 --> 01:20:58.992
More than conquerors. Greater is He that is in me than he that is in the world.

01:20:58.993 --> 01:21:11.262
I'm not living in fear. Fear tolerated is faith contaminated, and I will not live in fear. I walk by faith and not by sight.

01:21:11.263 --> 01:21:18.940
I'm a believing believer that has authority over the devil, but I listen to the voice of the Spirit of God.

01:21:18.941 --> 01:21:24.879
And when He says do it, do it. Follow Him in every area of your life.

01:21:24.880 --> 01:21:30.461
You know, Jack Coe, they—there was all these people, they had a big rainstorm coming in.

01:21:30.462 --> 01:21:42.713
Jack Coe had a big tent revival in Kansas, and he had this tent set up and there were tens of thousands of people coming and getting born again.

01:21:42.714 --> 01:21:54.238
Well, in the middle of the night, the Lord said, "Take that tent down right now and put it in the back of those semis and get out of there."Well, he had a meeting the next day and everybody was coming.

01:21:54.239 --> 01:21:59.000
Thousands of people were coming to this meeting to get healed and set free.

01:21:59.001 --> 01:22:12.590
But he heard in the middle of the night, the Spirit of the Lord told him, "I want you to take your tent, take it down, put it in the back of those semis and get out of here quick."Well, he told all the people the next day, "I'm sorry, we're canceling the meeting.

01:22:12.591 --> 01:22:23.158
The Lord said to take down the tent and pack it up and get out of here quick."And the pastors and the people around there said, "Well, you're not hearing God.

01:22:23.159 --> 01:22:26.251
Why would God say to do that? There's so many people getting born again.

01:22:26.252 --> 01:22:34.275
There's so many people getting healed. You're missing it, brother."And Jack said, "I'm sorry. I have an urgency.

01:22:34.276 --> 01:22:40.795
We must take the tent down."And all the other believers around there saying, "You're hearing the devil.

01:22:40.796 --> 01:22:46.204
That's you. Just take your authority. Just take your authority, Jack. Everything's going to be okay.

01:22:46.205 --> 01:23:02.647
That's just the devil trying to run you out of here."He said, "Well, you say what you want to, but I'm taking my tent down."So he took the tent down, and all of a sudden, the levees, the dike, the bridge, the dam broke in that valley.

01:23:02.648 --> 01:23:10.728
And in just a matter of minutes, he had 40 men lifting up that tent and putting it in there.

01:23:10.729 --> 01:23:14.238
They were trying to flee and get away. And he said, "Please don't leave me.

01:23:14.239 --> 01:23:22.008
Help me put my tent inside of the truck."So those 40 men lifted that up there and they got out just in time.

01:23:22.009 --> 01:23:32.850
He said he was looking in the rearview mirror, and where he was was completely flooded and destroyed.

01:23:32.851 --> 01:23:38.412
And if he would have been there, he would have lost his tent and all those people that were in that revival would have died.

01:23:38.413 --> 01:23:49.512
They would have drowned. The people that stayed and did not listen drowned. Churches were washed out. People died by the thousands.

01:23:49.513 --> 01:23:56.138
And so I just want to let you know, you say, "Well, that's torment, that's whatever."You take your authority.

01:23:56.139 --> 01:24:04.718
Jack Coe, he was a man, a mighty man of God. And I'm just saying, don't get flaky.

01:24:04.719 --> 01:24:14.559
Don't be in presumption. Hear Him and hear Him again. Listen to the voice of God and He'll protect you.

01:24:14.560 --> 01:24:27.919
Don't take that flight. Don't drive down that road. Listen to Him and listen again. Don't go to that event.

01:24:27.920 --> 01:24:42.238
I just try to tell you this because I hear a lot of people get real flaky with stuff, and we've got to stay grounded and stay in the Word and don't just be listening to all kinds of voices.

01:24:42.239 --> 01:24:50.439
Listen to one voice: the Holy Spirit. But the people I hear, they email us and say, "Well, you know, I hear an audible voice talk to me all the time"and all this stuff.

01:24:50.440 --> 01:24:56.556
I'm going to tell you, you know how many times Brandon has heard an audible voice of the Spirit of God talking to him—I'm talking about an audible voice?

01:24:56.557 --> 01:25:04.291
Never. In fact, well, I'd say once. I've heard it one time. But out of all the time I've been born again, I never hear an audible voice.

01:25:04.292 --> 01:25:10.853
The Lord does not talk to me in an audible voice. He talks to me in the still, small voice on the inside of me.

01:25:10.854 --> 01:25:17.039
And the more you pay attention to the still, small voice, that still, small voice gets loud.

01:25:17.040 --> 01:25:23.279
And it's no longer still and small to me; it's loud. I hear Him like I'm hearing you.

01:25:23.280 --> 01:25:29.143
He talks to me and we talk all the time. He will talk all the time to you.

01:25:29.144 --> 01:25:36.319
He has an opinion about everything. The Holy Spirit has an opinion about everything.

01:25:36.320 --> 01:25:42.479
But the more you have a relationship with Him, the more He will become real to you.

01:25:42.480 --> 01:25:50.861
When you get real with God, God will become real to you. And He will talk to you in the still, small voice inside of you.

01:25:50.862 --> 01:25:56.853
It's not weird, you know, "Oh, I hear voices out here."Those are devils.

01:25:56.854 --> 01:26:04.146
99.9% of the time, I can probably guarantee you, you're listening to demonic spirits.

01:26:04.147 --> 01:26:13.730
He's the still, small voice inside of you, and He'll talk to you through His Word.

01:26:13.731 --> 01:26:22.479
Get in this Bible and read it. And the more you read it, I'm telling you, it's an enlightenment.

01:26:22.480 --> 01:26:29.872
The eyes of your understanding will be enlightened. The Bible's a lamp unto my feet and a light unto my path.

01:26:29.873 --> 01:26:33.005
I will hide the Word in my heart that I might not sin against Him.

01:26:33.006 --> 01:26:37.966
So, get that Word down inside of you and pray and pray some more and fast.

01:26:37.967 --> 01:26:44.079
If you say, "Well, I don't hear God,"fast a little bit. Make your flesh squirm.

01:26:44.080 --> 01:26:51.839
Read your Bible, pray, and you'll hear Him. Practice His presence.

01:26:51.840 --> 01:27:00.458
Practice the Father's presence. I practice it. I talk to Him just like I'm talking to Braden right there.

01:27:00.459 --> 01:27:08.718
I talk to Him. My kids know I don't act all hyperspiritual and all weird and hermeneutical or theosophical.

01:27:08.719 --> 01:27:13.089
I'm just an old country guy who has been raised in a Christian home.

01:27:13.090 --> 01:27:22.436
You have to be hungry for it and you have to be thirsty. And He said, "Those that knock, He will open the door.

01:27:22.438 --> 01:27:31.359
Those that thirst, He will give you a drink."Remember, you're pursuing Him.

01:27:31.360 --> 01:27:39.198
How desperate are you for change? How thirsty, how hungry are you for change in your life?

01:27:39.199 --> 01:27:46.959
"Blessed are the pure in heart, for they will see God."That's Jesus.

01:27:46.960 --> 01:27:54.864
But I just want to give you an encouraging word today. Thank you for helping me pray this morning.

01:27:54.865 --> 01:28:05.279
I appreciate every single one of you for always being a part of this and coming and taking it seriously.

01:28:05.280 --> 01:28:13.582
I don't take it for granted ever that anyone would come and pray with me and just be a part of our prayer channel. We're growing every day.

01:28:13.583 --> 01:28:23.684
We're almost to 570,000 people, and we're so grateful for every single one of you that subscribe and are a part of this prayer channel.

01:28:23.685 --> 01:28:29.755
We have been praying for a million, and I believe the power of prayer changes things.

01:28:29.756 --> 01:28:45.071
We didn't realize Diana said, "Isn't it so neat that Kathryn Kuhlman named her whole organization Prayer Changes Things?"We didn't know when we named ours Prayer Changes Things; that was just leading by the Holy Spirit.

01:28:45.072 --> 01:28:52.479
And I said, because it's somebody we admire, I said, "That is wonderful, Diana.

01:28:52.480 --> 01:29:04.208
Look what the Lord did, even when we didn't know what He was doing—just following the leading of the Holy Spirit inside of you."He has such great plans for every single one of you.

01:29:04.209 --> 01:29:12.482
He loves every single one of you so much. And He's coming. Do you know Jesus is coming?

01:29:12.483 --> 01:29:18.156
He's standing at the door, ladies and gentlemen. He's coming, but He's wanting a harvest.

01:29:18.157 --> 01:29:24.215
He's leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one right now. So you pray.

01:29:24.216 --> 01:29:31.571
And like Sister Billye said last night, she talked about interceding for the unsaved.

01:29:31.572 --> 01:29:49.839
And you'll be surprised when you get over there who made it because of your prayers—interceding for your cousins, for your aunts, for your uncles, for your grandmas, for your grandpas, for your moms, your dads, your wife, your children.

01:29:49.840 --> 01:29:58.079
You're going to be—it's going to be—I'm telling you, He said that He wished that none should perish, but all come to repentance.

01:29:58.080 --> 01:30:04.994
And I believe that today your unsaved loved ones are going to have an experience with God.

01:30:04.995 --> 01:30:16.718
So, just have an expectation for it. It's time. We're going to start to see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

01:30:16.719 --> 01:30:30.295
Billy Graham, what he did is nothing compared to what we're about to see, and he did a lot—his tent meetings and his things.

01:30:30.296 --> 01:30:37.123
I believe that what we're about to see is going to be like, "Wow,"you know?

01:30:37.124 --> 01:30:46.994
It's time to believe God for bigger. So, God bless you all. I think that's good today for right now.

01:30:46.995 --> 01:30:54.990
I might come on this evening; depends on what I'm feeling this afternoon.

01:30:54.991 --> 01:30:58.803
But I wanted to say, I don't know if it's really a happy Yom Kippur.

01:30:58.804 --> 01:31:06.238
I don't even know if it's, you know, I know it's the Day of Repentance, a Day of Atonement, right?

01:31:06.239 --> 01:31:12.513
So glory to God for His mercy that we have Him now. He's our atoner.

01:31:12.514 --> 01:31:17.255
He washed all our sins in His precious blood. We don't have to have a goat.

01:31:17.256 --> 01:31:21.678
We don't have to have a sheep. We don't have to have a scapegoat go up the side of a mountain.

01:31:21.679 --> 01:31:29.434
We have Jesus. And Jesus paid the price for all our sins and all our sickness and all our disease.

01:31:29.435 --> 01:31:40.466
He paid the price for all of us to walk in victory, that we can come to His throne boldly and sit down and say, "Dad, how are you doing today?

01:31:40.467 --> 01:31:51.012
Jesus, how are you doing today?"If it wasn't for the blood of Jesus, every one of us would be lost.

01:31:51.013 --> 01:31:57.759
If it wasn't for the blood of Jesus, none of us could walk in divine health.

01:31:57.760 --> 01:32:06.559
I know it was the blood. I know it was the blood. I know it was the blood for me.

01:32:06.560 --> 01:32:14.716
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross. And I know it was the blood for me.

01:32:14.717 --> 01:32:23.599
He's coming back again. He's coming back again. He's coming back again for me.

01:32:23.600 --> 01:32:31.338
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross. And I know it was the blood for me.

01:32:31.339 --> 01:32:38.262
I believe that's the way the words go. "Three days and He arose.

01:32:38.263 --> 01:32:55.039
Three days and He arose."I love those old songs. He's coming back again for me.

01:32:55.040 --> 01:33:14.638
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross. They need to start singing stuff like that again.

01:33:14.639 --> 01:33:20.605
Well, did you get blessed today by it? Praise the Lord, I hope you did.

01:33:20.606 --> 01:33:32.851
I was blessed. He's coming back again for me. I know it was the blood.

01:33:32.852 --> 01:33:48.879
I know it was the blood. I know it was the blood for me. He shed the blood for me. He shed the blood for you. Do you believe it?

01:33:48.880 --> 01:33:58.730
One day when I was lost, Jesus died on the cross, and He's coming back again for me.

01:33:58.731 --> 01:34:07.591
I like those old songs; they get you dancing. Nancy's coming to our church.

01:34:07.592 --> 01:34:18.479
Nancy Dufresne's coming to the church this next week all for a bunch of days. Then Billy Burke, you follow Tennessee.

01:34:18.480 --> 01:34:30.740
The prayer conference is the fifteenth, sixteenth, seventeenth, eighteenth, nineteenth, and twentieth in Branson, Missouri—Sister Billye Brim, her prayer conference.

01:34:30.741 --> 01:34:38.383
And boy, are they going to have a meeting. They're going to have special guests there, Lynne Hammond.

01:34:38.384 --> 01:34:51.405
It's going to be wonderful. I'm excited about it. We're going to go and get in the prayer flow. There's a lot of good intercessors.

01:34:51.406 --> 01:34:56.957
They all assemble together, and boy, I tell you what, you can feel the river when they all pray.

01:34:56.958 --> 01:35:03.351
I just love it. You learn to cut your teeth on that kind of stuff. It's just changed my life.

01:35:03.352 --> 01:35:16.319
Why I am who I am was listening to Sister Lynne and Lucy and Billye and all the greats.

01:35:16.320 --> 01:35:24.559
It's where you learn. You've got to learn from the elders. And I'm telling you, it'll change your life.

01:35:24.560 --> 01:35:38.879
Don't go Rambo, you know. So, glory to God. Anybody have any questions or anything before I go?

01:35:38.880 --> 01:35:50.297
Excuse me. Do you see any comments? Nothing. You want to know anything?

01:35:50.298 --> 01:36:03.839
If not, I can't really go into a lot of what it's about today until I talk to my friend.

01:36:03.840 --> 01:36:28.319
But praise the Lord, no. "What does Jesus look like? What does Jesus look like?"Yeah, I'll tell you.

01:36:28.320 --> 01:36:43.439
This is it. Every time I think about what I saw, His eyes are pure pools of love.

01:36:43.440 --> 01:36:57.759
You can get lost in His eyes. They're the most crystal clear eyes I've ever looked into.

01:36:57.760 --> 01:37:13.839
The way He looks at you is the most yearning and love I can ever describe of anything I've ever seen. When He looks at you, He looks right through you.

01:37:13.840 --> 01:37:39.198
When He looks at you, the purity of who He is, it's—when you say love, His eyes are the expression of love.

01:37:39.199 --> 01:37:49.381
They're the most beautiful blue-green looking color I've ever seen.

01:37:49.382 --> 01:38:07.599
But there's no end to them. His hair goes real tailored to about right here, but it's tailored.

01:38:07.600 --> 01:38:15.919
It's very manicured and it's a beautiful brown color. His beard is perfect.

01:38:15.920 --> 01:38:22.399
His beard is very tailored and perfect. It's not long and bushy; it's tailored.

01:38:22.400 --> 01:38:39.678
Everything about Him, His skin tone is an olive. It's not white like Brandon; it's more of a brown, like an olive.

01:38:39.679 --> 01:38:52.673
But His beard is a brown; it's not black. It's brown like the shade of His hair, but His eyes are a blue, like a green-blue.

01:38:52.674 --> 01:39:00.982
They're the most piercing color of blue I've ever seen, like a beautiful color.

01:39:00.983 --> 01:39:09.999
They were not brown; they looked blue to me. And you know what? Remember whenever I had the throne experience?

01:39:10.000 --> 01:39:23.678
The eye that came out of the eye was like an all-seeing eye, but it came out and there was fire dancing in the middle of it.

01:39:23.679 --> 01:39:43.039
Fire was moving all inside of the eye. It wasn't one fire; it was hundreds of fires burning all inside of the eye because He was a consuming fire.

01:39:43.040 --> 01:39:54.559
The fire was dancing upon fire as I looked into it. And it was everything I could do not to wet myself.

01:39:54.560 --> 01:40:01.843
I'm not trying to be funny; I'm just being real with you. It was the most fearful thing I've ever seen in my life.

01:40:01.844 --> 01:40:22.959
I literally thought I was going to die. The fire was the most consuming fire, and the eyes were fire.

01:40:22.960 --> 01:40:35.678
And His voice was so thunderous that I thought it was going to pierce the inside of me when He spoke.

01:40:35.679 --> 01:40:53.279
And He said, "I am that I am."That's what He said. And it was so loud that it shook the very room that I was in: "I am that I am."And it went "woo".

01:40:53.280 --> 01:41:02.079
When He spoke, it went "woo". And every one of His words never died; they turned into a seed in front of my face.

01:41:02.080 --> 01:41:15.759
And as He spoke, they all gathered in lines. And they all started to sprout like a peanut before me, like spider vines.

01:41:15.760 --> 01:41:24.614
And every word became a word, and it never died. And it grew in front of my face as He spoke, and it formed sentences.

01:41:24.615 --> 01:41:30.769
And as the words were coming out, they grew together, and all the words grew together.

01:41:30.770 --> 01:41:41.192
And they went straight down, and the river of it was flowing through His throne. It was a river of water.

01:41:41.193 --> 01:41:52.158
And the roots and the words that came forth out of His mouth, they grew into the water and they grew a taproot into the water and they never died.

01:41:52.159 --> 01:41:59.999
Every word that he spoke became a plant, like a growth of something coming out, and it grew.

01:42:00.000 --> 01:42:17.359
His words never die. They're always alive. They don't return unto him void. He doesn't flippantly talk.

01:42:17.360 --> 01:42:33.580
His words become alive in the seed, and they spring forth life as he speaks, and they grow into the water, and the water flows from his throne.

01:42:33.581 --> 01:42:45.439
And there's ankle-deep, waist-deep, and there's over-the-head deep, clear at his throne—the clearest, purest water you've ever seen in your life.

01:42:45.440 --> 01:42:59.359
No pollution, no nothing. It's the most beautiful water. And there's plants that are growing into that water.

01:42:59.360 --> 01:43:13.359
I could see the seeds. And as he spoke, they kept growing, and they went up together, and it looked like a whole...

01:43:13.360 --> 01:43:19.279
I told you there were hieroglyphics and writing I've never seen before.

01:43:19.280 --> 01:43:28.158
They were all on these tablets on the side, and I could see writing, and it was etched in this stone. It looked like granite.

01:43:28.159 --> 01:43:44.112
It was all on the side of his throne, and I could see the words that were written looked like they were etched by his hand, like you would see like Moses'tablets, but it was writing like I've never seen before.

01:43:44.113 --> 01:44:00.479
And there were all kinds of different shapes and things. It looked like something from like what you'd see in Egyptian hieroglyphics.

01:44:00.480 --> 01:44:08.079
It was a writing. I don't understand it, but it was all etched in the side of this rock.

01:44:08.080 --> 01:44:15.759
I don't know why he let me see that, but they were there and he pointed it out to me.

01:44:15.760 --> 01:44:27.519
It was ancient and upon his head. His crown has three major stones.

01:44:27.520 --> 01:44:37.063
They were blue as sapphire. And upon his head was a crown that looked like a sapphire.

01:44:37.064 --> 01:44:44.079
This massive fire was coming out of him, and he allowed me to see inside of him.

01:44:44.080 --> 01:45:03.439
And he's endless. There is no beginning and there is no end. But there's sparkles of light, and he is a dimension in himself.

01:45:03.440 --> 01:45:20.158
He said, "I want to let you see,"and he let me. Whether you believe or don't believe, I don't really care what you believe. I'm telling you what I saw.

01:45:20.159 --> 01:45:37.599
And upon his head were stones, three major stones, and I got to see inside of it, and they were blue and they were gorgeous.

01:45:37.600 --> 01:45:59.539
The most beautiful thing I've ever seen, and I beheld it. But inside of him, there was no beginning and there was no end.

01:45:59.540 --> 01:46:21.039
He was a dimension. He is God, Jehovah our God, from his throne, and his eyes are a flaming fire. He is a consuming fire.

01:46:21.040 --> 01:46:33.678
And upon his throne, the angels go around, and they were singing, "Holy, holy, holy is the Lord of hosts, who was and is and is to come.

01:46:33.679 --> 01:46:48.319
Holy, holy, holy is the Lord of hosts, who was and is and is to come."And as they said it, it shook the foundation of everything.

01:46:48.320 --> 01:46:54.713
Did you hear that? Yeah. Was that thunder when I said that, son?

01:46:54.715 --> 01:47:16.392
Yeah, that was over the top. That gave me chills. Whoa. Wow. Praise God.

01:47:16.393 --> 01:47:32.079
Whoa. Did you hear that? When I said that, every prayer when we pray looks like a ball of fire.

01:47:32.080 --> 01:47:46.184
It circles his throne, and they go inside of him, and he breathes them in. I watched him as we pray, interceding for the world.

01:47:46.185 --> 01:48:00.525
They come up, and they look like comets, and they circle his throne, and he breathes the prayers in, and they come out, and they circle, and they don't die.

01:48:00.526 --> 01:48:12.879
The prayers continually are fire, and I could see them coming in and out of him, and he would breathe and it would circle.

01:48:12.880 --> 01:48:19.210
I remember seeing a man praying for intercession, and he allowed me to hear this.

01:48:19.211 --> 01:48:28.479
Pastor Tracy Harris was interceding for the nations, and Pastor Tracy Harris was praying for the nations, and I was allowed to hear him.

01:48:28.480 --> 01:48:42.912
He has a church in Texarkana, and he was in the throne room with me that day and didn't know I could hear him praying, and the Lord allowed me to hear Pastor Tracy Harris praying in the throne room.

01:48:42.913 --> 01:48:54.799
He was interceding for the world, and I saw an impartation going to that man that day.

01:48:54.800 --> 01:49:03.919
I have these experiences and I don't talk about them very often, but you asked.

01:49:03.920 --> 01:49:12.799
But there is no beginning and there is no end. There is no time. He is God.

01:49:12.800 --> 01:49:35.839
And for what little glimpse I got to see that day, oh, he looks like a massive eye.

01:49:35.840 --> 01:49:49.636
There are no words that can can describe. I tried my best, even with what I said to you today.

01:49:49.637 --> 01:49:59.599
He is light, and in him, there is no darkness at all. He is light.

01:49:59.600 --> 01:50:09.759
But once you get past the outer layer—there's a layer of... okay, I'll try my best.

01:50:09.760 --> 01:50:25.944
His skin is light, okay? But inside of him... we're made in his image, okay?

01:50:25.945 --> 01:50:35.359
So you look at it like this: you take the sun, and you look at the sun, and the sun is dark compared to what he looked like.

01:50:35.360 --> 01:50:54.079
But once you can get past the light, we are made in his image. We are made like him.

01:50:54.080 --> 01:51:09.839
He looks like us or we look like him, just like Jesus. He has form.

01:51:09.840 --> 01:51:25.039
But once you get past the layer of light, he is a dimension. There is no beginning and there is no end.

